<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.2.10">
<l>eṉceykē ṉeṉṉuṭaip pētaiyeṉ kōmaḷa</l>
<l>meṉcollu meṉvaca mumalla ṇaṅkaimīr</l>
<l>miṉceypūṇ mārpiṉaṉ kaṇṇaṉ kaḻaṟuḻāy</l>
<l>poṉceypūṇ meṉmulaik keṉṟu meliyumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What will I do with my foolish girl? My tender one,</l>
<l>not heeding my words and authority, you ladies,</l>
<l>weakens, saying “for [my] soft breast with golden ornaments</l>
<l>the Tulsi from the anklet of Kaṇṇaṉ, on [his] chest flashing ornaments.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
